 :notes
 ["This solution is intentionally the cross-cutting middleware map. Specific host-owned primitives remain in their own solution documents: raw signal access, module store, bounded local server runtime, capability binding, Dator, Arca, Sensorium, and Memarium."
  "The diagram in `019-middleware.md` is the canonical high-level hook map. It should be updated whenever a new middleware input chain or dispatch surface becomes first-class."]}
